WEBVTT

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:06.430
I'm so thankful that there are so many of

00:08:06.440 --> 00:08:08.270
you who want to pray with us this late

00:08:08.280 --> 00:08:10.270
at night.

00:08:10.280 --> 00:08:12.830
Welcome and good evening,

00:08:12.840 --> 00:08:15.150
family. Good early morning to all of

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:16.310
you.

00:08:17.760 --> 00:08:19.750
I'm going to go over some of the things

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:21.909
the Lord showed us in this last video.

00:08:21.919 --> 00:08:25.030
I was praying over

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:29.470
some of the correction the Lord

00:08:29.470 --> 00:08:29.480
gave me;

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:31.950
He corrected me on

00:08:31.960 --> 00:08:34.390
how I communicate

00:08:34.390 --> 00:08:34.400
because

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:37.070
I don't want to bring fear to you.

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:38.589
He said, 'Brandon, don't bring

00:08:38.599 --> 00:08:41.390
fear to their hearts. Warn them

00:08:41.400 --> 00:08:43.589
and walk away from

00:08:43.589 --> 00:08:43.599
it.'You

00:08:43.599 --> 00:08:44.990
don't have to

00:08:45.000 --> 00:08:46.670
scare the

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:48.910
elderly

00:08:48.920 --> 00:08:50.990
or

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:52.350
the young;

00:08:54.040 --> 00:08:56.990
just present what I show you and walk

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:58.110
away.

00:08:58.120 --> 00:09:00.670
How they handle it is between Me

00:09:00.680 --> 00:09:01.750
and them. It

00:09:01.750 --> 00:09:01.760
is about

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:04.270
how you

00:09:04.280 --> 00:09:06.630
communicate, and I'm

00:09:06.640 --> 00:09:07.750
learning.

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:09.430
When it comes to

00:09:09.440 --> 00:09:11.270
the plague and the things the Lord has

00:09:11.270 --> 00:09:11.280
shown

00:09:11.280 --> 00:09:13.870
me, I truly believe with all my

00:09:13.880 --> 00:09:15.390
heart that when you are in the cleft of the

00:09:15.400 --> 00:09:17.470
rock, no weapon formed against

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:19.230
you is going to prosper.

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:21.230
I always want to drive that home:

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:24.110
God always provides a

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:26.790
way of escape for the believer. He

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:29.510
showed Joseph

00:09:29.520 --> 00:09:32.350
the seven years of plenty and the seven years of

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:35.350
famine. He showed Noah to build the

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:37.870
ark.

00:09:37.880 --> 00:09:39.390
He's always had a way. He's the

00:09:39.390 --> 00:09:39.400
waymaker.

00:09:39.400 --> 00:09:41.550
He will always provide the

00:09:41.560 --> 00:09:43.750
way. He doesn't leave His kids high and

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:47.470
dry and say, 'Well, you know what?

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:49.990
You're on your own,

00:09:49.990 --> 00:09:50.000
pal.'He's

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.710
always there saying, 'I love you and

00:09:51.720 --> 00:09:53.590
I've got a plan for your

00:09:53.590 --> 00:09:53.600
life.'That's

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:55.590
why I try to tell you, you can't derail

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:57.910
your life if you're seeking Jesus. If

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.470
your heart

00:10:00.470 --> 00:10:00.480
is

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:02.550
seeking Him, the Bible

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:04.550
says, 'Those that seek Me will find

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:04.560
Me.'What

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:06.630
the devil meant

00:10:06.640 --> 00:10:08.590
for bad, God will turn around for good

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:09.950
in your life.

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:12.790
If you're actively pursuing Him,

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:15.270
you will find Him.

00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:17.070
If you're being lazy and sitting on

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:18.830
your 'blessed assurance'and not

00:10:18.840 --> 00:10:20.390
pursuing the Lord or having a

00:10:20.400 --> 00:10:22.310
relationship with Him,

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:23.950
His hands are tied on some things, but

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:27.950
He'll keep that nudging at your heart.

00:10:27.960 --> 00:10:30.790
My dad was telling me tonight

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:33.670
about growing potatoes in sacks and

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:36.790
having creative ideas for

00:10:36.790 --> 00:10:36.800
it.

00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:38.310
He said he put

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:41.350
dirt in the sack, and

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:43.910
one

00:10:43.920 --> 00:10:46.630
sack produces 100 pounds in a gunny sack. He

00:10:46.640 --> 00:10:47.670
said, 'Son, I'm going to be able to

00:10:47.680 --> 00:10:51.230
produce 100 pounds per sack of potatoes, and

00:10:51.230 --> 00:10:51.240
with

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:53.510
three sacks, that'll be 300 pounds of

00:10:53.520 --> 00:10:55.910
potatoes when it's all said and

00:10:55.910 --> 00:10:55.920
done.'Dad's

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:57.470
always thinking and prepping.

00:10:59.040 --> 00:11:00.190
It's interesting

00:11:00.190 --> 00:11:00.200
because

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:02.430
everybody is listening to the Lord for

00:11:02.430 --> 00:11:02.440
themselves

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:04.990
and what He's telling them to

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.110
do.

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:08.270
Is there fear in that? No.

00:11:08.280 --> 00:11:09.790
My dad's not afraid; people aren't

00:11:09.800 --> 00:11:11.630
afraid. When you're listening to the

00:11:11.640 --> 00:11:13.950
voice of the Lord, He will lead and

00:11:13.960 --> 00:11:15.590
guide you on what you're supposed to be

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.710
doing.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:18.630
Whenever He spoke to the people

00:11:18.630 --> 00:11:18.640
about

00:11:18.640 --> 00:11:21.310
turning water into wine,

00:11:21.320 --> 00:11:23.350
Mary said, 'Whatever He tells

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:25.350
you to do, do

00:11:25.350 --> 00:11:25.360
it.'They

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:28.430
followed His instruction.

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:37.270
He could instruct you to do

00:11:37.280 --> 00:11:39.110
something totally different than what

00:11:39.120 --> 00:11:40.630
He's telling my dad.

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:42.390
The Lord didn't tell me to

00:11:42.390 --> 00:11:42.400
use

00:11:42.400 --> 00:11:44.390
a gunny sack full of potatoes, but He's

00:11:44.400 --> 00:11:46.310
talking to my dad about it.

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:48.070
I thought that was interesting.

00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:50.070
You have to follow the voice of God for

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:53.630
what He's telling you to do.

00:11:53.640 --> 00:11:55.390
When I'm bringing up things

00:11:55.400 --> 00:11:58.190
about the end times, whether you live in New

00:11:58.200 --> 00:11:59.710
York,

00:11:59.720 --> 00:12:01.950
Oklahoma,

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:03.310
or

00:12:03.320 --> 00:12:05.310
California,

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:10.670
your

00:12:10.680 --> 00:12:12.350
instruction is going to be different

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:14.270
than mine because

00:12:14.280 --> 00:12:16.430
you live in a different area or climate.

00:12:21.360 --> 00:12:23.590
You just have to

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:24.990
follow the voice.

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:26.830
As

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:29.670
the major scripture for last night

00:12:29.670 --> 00:12:29.680
says,

00:12:29.680 --> 00:12:32.030
'For those that are led by the Spirit of

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:36.910
God are the sons and daughters of

00:12:36.910 --> 00:12:36.920
God.'I

00:12:36.920 --> 00:12:39.750
believe with all my heart that you

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:42.030
don't need a prophetic voice

00:12:42.040 --> 00:12:43.670
holding your hand.

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:50.070
His sheep will hear His

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:52.270
voice, and a stranger's voice they will not

00:12:52.280 --> 00:12:57.070
follow.

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:59.430
You have to be His

00:12:59.430 --> 00:12:59.440
and

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:01.230
abide

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:04.310
in Him. 'If ye abide in Me and

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:06.190
My words remain in you, you will ask

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:08.070
what you will and it shall be

00:13:08.070 --> 00:13:08.080
done.'There

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:11.070
are

00:13:11.080 --> 00:13:13.070
qualifications for a

00:13:13.080 --> 00:13:15.430
relationship with God: abiding in His

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:16.630
Word

00:13:16.630 --> 00:13:16.640
and

00:13:16.640 --> 00:13:18.510
having fellowship with Him daily.

00:13:20.480 --> 00:13:23.630
It takes practice

00:13:23.630 --> 00:13:23.640
and

00:13:23.640 --> 00:13:26.829
time. Practice His presence. Spend time

00:13:26.839 --> 00:13:29.030
with the Father every day in

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:31.270
prayer and reading His

00:13:31.280 --> 00:13:32.390
Word.

00:13:32.400 --> 00:13:34.550
Get into the scripture and

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:36.750
make it real to you.

00:13:36.760 --> 00:13:38.590
When it becomes rhema to you, that's

00:13:38.600 --> 00:13:40.590
whenever it will work for you.

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:43.190
Until then, you're just parroting.

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:45.470
You have a relationship because of intimacy with Him, not just because

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:47.590
your pastor tells you to.

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:52.310
Everything is about intimacy with Him.

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:55.710
If your pastor

00:13:55.720 --> 00:13:58.550
or

00:13:58.560 --> 00:14:00.870
spiritual leader dies

00:14:00.880 --> 00:14:02.670
tomorrow,

00:14:04.640 --> 00:14:07.110
do you have an

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:08.750
intimate relationship or will it

00:14:08.760 --> 00:14:11.590
completely derail you?

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:15.230
You must find Jesus for yourself.

00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:17.870
Your pastor can't get you there;

00:14:17.880 --> 00:14:20.670
your relative can't get

00:14:20.680 --> 00:14:22.510
you there.

00:14:22.520 --> 00:14:23.950
You

00:14:23.960 --> 00:14:25.750
are the only one who will stand before

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:28.070
the Father alone.

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:35.110
I will stand before my Creator alone,

00:14:35.120 --> 00:14:37.750
and you must find Him alone.

00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:50.829
There's so much truth to the song

00:14:50.829 --> 00:14:50.839
'I Come

00:14:50.839 --> 00:14:54.750
to the Garden

00:14:54.750 --> 00:14:54.760
Alone.'When

00:14:54.760 --> 00:14:58.150
I tell you

00:14:58.160 --> 00:14:59.750
what the Lord is saying,

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:02.110
it's not to scare you.

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:03.950
We love

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:05.070
you,

00:15:05.080 --> 00:15:07.270
but if you're scared,

00:15:07.280 --> 00:15:08.510
I believe it's because He's trying to

00:15:08.520 --> 00:15:10.390
shake you to wake you up.

00:15:10.400 --> 00:15:12.510
On

00:15:12.520 --> 00:15:14.430
January 1,

00:15:14.440 --> 00:15:16.110
the Lord said

00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:19.350
2026 will be the year of 1 Corinthians

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:21.590
5:5.

00:15:21.600 --> 00:15:24.630
I am going to shake the church and

00:15:24.630 --> 00:15:24.640
its

00:15:24.640 --> 00:15:27.190
leadership. There

00:15:27.190 --> 00:15:27.200
will

00:15:27.200 --> 00:15:29.390
be people here at the

00:15:29.400 --> 00:15:31.950
beginning of the year who won't be here

00:15:31.960 --> 00:15:33.230
very long;

00:15:33.240 --> 00:15:34.870
they're about to go home.

00:15:37.400 --> 00:15:39.990
You will see great leaders in great

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:42.830
positions not be here anymore, and

00:15:42.830 --> 00:15:42.840
their

00:15:42.840 --> 00:15:46.070
ministries will soon close down.

00:15:46.080 --> 00:15:47.790
The

00:15:50.030 --> 00:15:50.040
Lord

00:15:52.640 --> 00:15:55.310
said

00:15:55.320 --> 00:15:58.030
judgment begins in the house of the

00:15:58.040 --> 00:16:00.710
Lord first. He said there's

00:16:00.720 --> 00:16:03.150
corruption in big ministries that I'm

00:16:03.160 --> 00:16:04.990
going to deal with this year.

00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:07.710
Some will be standing

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:09.550
behind pulpits and fall over

00:16:09.560 --> 00:16:11.190
dead right there, like Ananias and

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:13.150
Sapphira.

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:15.550
I saw people preaching,

00:16:15.550 --> 00:16:15.560
and

00:16:15.560 --> 00:16:17.230
they went

00:16:17.240 --> 00:16:19.790
home right there.

00:16:19.800 --> 00:16:21.830
The Lord said there will be

00:16:21.830 --> 00:16:21.840
mega-ministries

00:16:21.840 --> 00:16:25.550
that

00:16:25.560 --> 00:16:28.070
will no longer be here this year.

00:16:28.070 --> 00:16:28.080
There

00:16:28.080 --> 00:16:29.790
will

00:16:29.800 --> 00:16:31.270
be

00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:34.070
transitions in ministries,

00:16:34.080 --> 00:16:35.230
and they'll say, 'What about

00:16:35.240 --> 00:16:36.750
my legacy?

00:16:36.760 --> 00:16:38.829
Who's going to take over

00:16:38.839 --> 00:16:40.990
after I'm

00:16:46.630 --> 00:16:46.640
gone?'I

00:17:04.120 --> 00:17:07.309
see these generals going

00:17:07.319 --> 00:17:08.590
home

00:17:08.600 --> 00:17:11.550
and new Davids rising up. I see a

00:17:11.560 --> 00:17:14.510
passing of the baton

00:17:14.520 --> 00:17:17.510
coming on an even greater

00:17:17.520 --> 00:17:20.390
scale.

00:17:22.839 --> 00:17:24.510
I waited as they asked me to stay

00:17:24.520 --> 00:17:26.189
longer.

00:17:27.560 --> 00:17:29.550
But

00:17:29.560 --> 00:17:31.750
the door is coming

00:17:31.760 --> 00:17:33.910
and a passing of the baton. I see

00:17:33.910 --> 00:17:33.920
a

00:17:33.920 --> 00:17:35.830
certain general asking

00:17:35.830 --> 00:17:35.840
to

00:17:35.840 --> 00:17:37.870
stay longer. Could he stay longer? Because

00:17:37.870 --> 00:17:37.880
he told them

00:17:37.880 --> 00:17:39.310
they're coming home. And he said,

00:17:39.320 --> 00:17:41.790
"No, this time you'll

00:17:41.800 --> 00:17:43.990
see a passing of the baton.

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:47.190
A door will open, they will

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:50.270
walk through, and there will be a passing of the baton.

00:17:50.280 --> 00:17:53.230
It was about their legacy.

00:17:53.240 --> 00:17:55.830
The Lord said it was about legacy. They

00:17:55.830 --> 00:17:55.840
asked him,

00:17:55.840 --> 00:17:58.670
'What will happen to my legacy?

00:18:00.600 --> 00:18:04.550
I must pray and cultivate to

00:18:04.560 --> 00:18:07.750
make sure of my legacy.'And now

00:18:07.760 --> 00:18:09.670
you'll

00:18:09.680 --> 00:18:12.430
see. They've been on borrowed time.

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:14.150
This is what they

00:18:14.160 --> 00:18:15.950
said because a new generation

00:18:15.950 --> 00:18:15.960
is

00:18:15.960 --> 00:18:18.710
coming and I see a passing of the baton.

00:18:18.720 --> 00:18:20.110
They would say, 'What about

00:18:20.110 --> 00:18:20.120
the

00:18:20.120 --> 00:18:21.710
legacy

00:18:21.720 --> 00:18:23.510
of what I leave

00:18:23.510 --> 00:18:23.520
with

00:18:23.520 --> 00:18:25.670
this

00:18:25.680 --> 00:18:26.670
ministry?'I

00:18:26.680 --> 00:18:28.630
hear this in the spirit realm. They'll

00:18:28.640 --> 00:18:31.750
start to go home.

00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:42.430
The Lord wouldn't let me talk

00:18:42.440 --> 00:18:44.310
about it because I saw the individual who it

00:18:44.320 --> 00:18:45.510
was

00:18:45.520 --> 00:18:47.470
and the Lord said, 'Don't you dare touch

00:18:47.480 --> 00:18:48.830
that.'And

00:18:48.840 --> 00:18:51.950
so the Lord told me to

00:18:51.960 --> 00:18:53.350
bring that up again. There will be

00:18:56.360 --> 00:18:59.030
a lot of transition coming

00:18:59.040 --> 00:19:01.510
in the days ahead.

00:19:01.520 --> 00:19:03.870
Mega ministers

00:19:03.880 --> 00:19:06.470
will soon go home.

00:19:06.480 --> 00:19:08.150
And the Lord said, 'Brandon, this is

00:19:08.160 --> 00:19:10.830
what a transition will be for 1

00:19:10.830 --> 00:19:10.840
Corinthians

00:19:10.840 --> 00:19:12.870
5:5. You will see

00:19:12.880 --> 00:19:15.150
a shaking that will awaken to bring

00:19:15.160 --> 00:19:19.830
the bride by my

00:19:19.830 --> 00:19:19.840
side.'I

00:19:19.840 --> 00:19:22.270
touched that lightly, but

00:19:22.280 --> 00:19:27.150
I want you to see this right here.

00:19:27.160 --> 00:19:30.190
This was

00:19:31.120 --> 00:19:33.550
January 23rd, 2026.

00:19:38.200 --> 00:19:41.950
I told you 1 Corinthians 5:5

00:19:41.960 --> 00:19:45.350
was the word

00:19:45.360 --> 00:19:48.990
of the Lord for 2026.

00:19:52.320 --> 00:19:53.430
A lot of people didn't want to hear

00:19:53.440 --> 00:19:55.750
that.

00:19:55.760 --> 00:19:57.230
But I said you're going to see great

00:19:57.240 --> 00:20:00.550
leaders in California fall. There will be

00:20:00.560 --> 00:20:03.990
great church shaking in California in

00:20:04.000 --> 00:20:06.950
the days ahead.

00:20:06.960 --> 00:20:09.150
A major leader of a major church in

00:20:09.160 --> 00:20:11.990
California will be shaken and things will be

00:20:12.000 --> 00:20:14.910
exposed.

00:20:20.240 --> 00:20:21.870
I said it will go all over the

00:20:21.880 --> 00:20:23.830
media,

00:20:23.840 --> 00:20:26.110
but I've not touched it.

00:20:28.400 --> 00:20:30.190
The Lord said, 'I'm shaking churches,

00:20:30.200 --> 00:20:31.390
Brandon.

00:20:31.400 --> 00:20:36.110
I'm exposing

00:20:36.110 --> 00:20:36.120
corruption.'He

00:20:36.120 --> 00:20:38.390
said, 'A major TV network won't be

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:40.350
there very much longer. They'll go down,

00:20:40.350 --> 00:20:40.360
too.'I've

00:20:40.360 --> 00:20:42.070
warned

00:20:42.070 --> 00:20:42.080
about

00:20:42.080 --> 00:20:44.510
this

00:20:44.520 --> 00:20:46.790
many times.

00:20:46.800 --> 00:20:49.070
There's corruption in TV networks,

00:20:49.080 --> 00:20:51.110
churches,

00:20:51.110 --> 00:20:51.120
and

