harvest of souls beyond anybody's

01:31:16.200 --> 01:31:18.350
comprehension is about to happen. We

01:31:18.360 --> 01:31:21.550
call that virus to die.

01:31:21.560 --> 01:31:23.830
And on that boat, we say in the name of

01:31:23.840 --> 01:31:28.550
Jesus, it's not time.

01:31:28.560 --> 01:31:32.830
We call you to die; virus, go away.

01:31:32.840 --> 01:31:35.750
We call for rain over our area today. We

01:31:35.760 --> 01:31:37.710
call rain from the north, the south,

01:31:37.710 --> 01:31:37.720
the

01:31:37.720 --> 01:31:40.990
east, the west. We call for our crops: rain,

01:31:41.000 --> 01:31:45.190
rain, rain in Jesus'name. We call in five

01:31:45.190 --> 01:31:45.200
inches.

01:31:45.200 --> 01:31:47.390
We call it in over their areas that

01:31:47.400 --> 01:31:49.790
there's no drought. We take authority

01:31:49.800 --> 01:31:52.150
over drought. We call the

01:31:52.150 --> 01:31:52.160
low-pressure

01:31:52.160 --> 01:31:55.350
systems to come in in the name of Jesus.

01:31:55.360 --> 01:31:57.790
We speak to the drought to go, and we

01:31:57.800 --> 01:32:01.830
call for Holy Ghost flow in Jesus'name. We

01:32:01.840 --> 01:32:03.670
thank you, Lord, that we're in the right

01:32:03.680 --> 01:32:05.590
place at the right time, and we give you

01:32:05.600 --> 01:32:07.590
all the glory, honor, and praise for it

01:32:07.600 --> 01:32:10.510
in the name of Jesus. Amen and amen.

01:32:10.520 --> 01:32:12.110
Well, if you prayed with us for even

01:32:12.120 --> 01:32:13.950
