01:32:13.960 --> 01:32:17.990
so grateful for every single one of you.

01:32:18.000 --> 01:32:20.230
It's been a good week. You know, we

01:32:20.240 --> 01:32:22.950
pushed. We got 46 people born again

01:32:22.960 --> 01:32:24.950
today, and we're so grateful for

01:32:24.960 --> 01:32:27.350
that, and it's been wonderful. We

01:32:27.360 --> 01:32:29.590
